<br>
&lt;&lt;&lt;<br>
A lot of mixed information can be found regarding which mobs (on drake island) drop crown and which mob drops it most frequently etc. For example one PoA guide says Undine Spirits are best for farming crowns. Here is how the 33 crowns (I know I said 32 crowns earlier but it is in fact 33 sorry) we looted was spread out among the different mob types.<br>
<br>
Heartsbane Drake = 9 crowns<br>
Greater Sphinx = 8 crowns<br>
Fatestealer Drake = 8 crowns<br>
Undine Spirits = 6 crowns<br>
Windrider Drake = 2 crowns<br>
<br>
Next is how many crowns dropped for every island clearing we did (17 clearings and a total of 33 crowns). <br>
<br>
Clearing 1 = 4 crowns <br>
Clearing 2 = 2 crowns<br>
Clearing 3 = 3 crowns<br>
Clearing 4 = 1 crown<br>
Clearing 5 = 0 crowns<br>
Clearing 6 = 1 crown<br>
Clearing 7 = 3 crowns<br>
Clearing 8 = 2 crowns<br>
Clearing 9 = 2 crowns<br>
Clearing 10 = 1 crown<br>
Clearing 11 = 4 crowns<br>
Clearing 12 = 2 crowns<br>
Clearing 13 = 2 crowns<br>
Clearing 14 = 0 crowns<br>
**Clearing 15 = 2 crown<br>
**Clearing 16 = 1 crown<br>
***Clearing 17 = 3 crowns<br>
<br>
** = Undine Spirits left alive<br>
*** = Various left alive because we all jumped off island <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
